
The frontend of the app presents an intuitive and interactive user interface,
designed to facilitate seamless communication. It features an authentication page for user login, 
transitioning to a chat interface upon successful login. This chat interface leverages the 
react-chat-engine-pretty for visually appealing chat windows, allowing users to engage in conversations in real time. 
Emphasizing user experience, the design is clean and responsive, ensuring accessibility across various devices. 
With a focus on simplicity and efficiency, the app aims to provide a user-friendly platform for effortless communication
